{"TopicId":174669,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"Navball Marker Issue","CreatedByName":"Leszek","CreatedById":119053,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T10:06:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Leszek","CreatedById":119053,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T10:06:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems that in the current version of KSP the Navball markers like to disappear when you are almost pointed at them.\u00A0 This causes me all sorts of headache but I can\u0027t find the option to turn this \u003Cspan\u003E\u0022feature\u0022 off.\u00A0 Anyone know how to do that?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T11:30:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts not like that, maybe a bug?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt works fine here, do you have any mods?Are you switching btw Surface and Orbit mode by accident?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Leszek","CreatedById":119053,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T11:50:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223372210\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174669\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525606203\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179192\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Boyster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, Boyster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts not like that, maybe a bug?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt works fine here, do you have any mods?Are you switching btw Surface and Orbit mode by accident?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have lots of mods but I can\u0027t think of one that would do that.\u00A0 Definitely not switching modes, all markers disappear when centered and they do that in both surface and orbital.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the mods, I have a mod less version in the steam folder, I will run that and see what happens.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpdate: Nope the clean steam install behaves the same way.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpdate again:\u00A0 I wonder if it is a bug and related to having a 4k monitor with GUI and Navball expanded to max?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-06T12:02:38Z\u0022 title=\u002205/06/2018 12:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 6, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Leszek\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T13:02:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223372224\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174669\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525607435\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119053\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Leszek\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Leszek said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUpdate again:\u00A0 I wonder if it is a bug and related to having a 4k monitor with GUI and Navball expanded to max?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConfirmed. It\u0027s when you set the UI scale to max. Thanks for the info.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Leszek","CreatedById":119053,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T13:04:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223372267\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174669\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525611766\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConfirmed. It\u0027s when you set the UI scale to max. Thanks for the info.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep I can confirm that is what I have, but setting to 140% fixes the issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess that makes it a bug.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-06T13:05:38Z\u0022 title=\u002205/06/2018 01:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 6, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Leszek\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T13:14:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSetting the Navball scale to 149% also fixes the issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Leszek","CreatedById":119053,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T13:28:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223372273\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174669\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525612451\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSetting the Navball scale to 149% also fixes the issue.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep for me too.\u00A0 I see you are a bug exterminator.\u00A0 Are you submitting the bug report?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-06T17:41:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, I put it in front of the devs -- they will investigate it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-07T16:08:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoving to Technical Support, since this sounds like a game bug.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}